examples.en: We sat in the shade of a willow tree.
She was slender as a willow shoot is slender.
examples.ru: Она была тоненькая, как ивовый прутик.

examples.en: ...the descendant branches of a weeping willow...
The interior was comparted by willow screens.
examples.ru: Внутри помещение было разделено ивовыми ширмами.

examples.en: The path was overhung with willow trees.
